body: What is the original framework that you are referring to? Did you run into any issues during conversion?

Hi @JaheimLee ,

We have HuggingFace / ONNX Runtime tutorials here: **https://onnxruntime.ai/docs/tutorials/huggingface.html**

Specifically on the BART export, there is a HuggingFace notebook here: https://github.com/huggingface/notebooks/blob/master/examples/onnx-export.ipynb, which runs the steps to export and compare performance between PyTorch and ONNX Runtime. You should be able to replace the steps for BERT with BART to get the results you need. Please let us know how you go.
